Good points.

I'm going to leave it a day so I can come back with fresher eyes, then try and add a little more menace. When I first had the idea, I wanted to move away from making it too aggressive, but I think I've gone too far the other way. Right now, it's just a thing. I want to make it an interesting thing.

One possible direction I may take this: making it react only to violence against people in Police uniform. Three D-Class could rape each other to death with flensing knives right in front of it, and SCP-912 wouldn't react at all. Someone patting someone in uniform on the back too hard? They get their elbow twisted up to the back of their skull.

Of course, I welcome suggestions. People on the forum weren't too forthcoming with ways I could punch this up a little.







